track_notes: Drive to the village AUVARE, this is a no-issue road, there is a car park at the entrance, the walk is easy in summer just need some water, in winter snowshoes if snow is there.

Nice place for radio, with a wide panorama.
Starting from the village AUVARE, the walk is easy until you reach the Col de Panegi√©re; then you must reach the final crest in between small trees, you can found some old painted marks and 1 or 2 cairn.
Plenty room for antenna on summit.
